{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_016u9tSp8stQBNiqFPeFCLQ3","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Session Retrospective — 2026-03-28\n     2→\n     3→## Session 51 — Sprint Complete, No-Op #35\n     4→\n     5→**Date:** 2026-03-28\n     6→**Session:** 51\n     7→**Sprint status:** COMPLETE — 74/74 stories done, 17/17 epics done\n     8→**Productive work this session:** None. State corruption fix only.\n     9→\n    10→---\n    11→\n    12→## Sprint Summary\n    13→\n    14→| Metric | Value |\n    15→|--------|-------|\n    16→| Total stories | 74 |\n    17→| Stories done | 74 |\n    18→| Total epics | 17 |\n    19→| Epics done | 17 |\n    20→| Sprint completed at | Session 30 |\n    21→| No-op sessions since completion | 35 (sessions 17-51) |\n    22→\n    23→## The Recurring Bug\n    24→\n    25→Every session since session 17, Ralph's stale in-memory state overwrites `sprint-state.json`, reverting stories 16-5, 16-6, 16-7, 16-8 from `done` to `review` and epic-16 from `done` to `backlog`. Each session detects the regression, fixes it, logs it, and exits. This is the 35th consecutive occurrence.\n    26→\n    27→**Root cause:** Ralph loads state at startup, holds it in memory, and writes it back on each loop iteration. The in-memory snapshot predates the completion of stories 16-5 through 16-8. The `registerStory` guard (session 22) prevents new phantom stories but does not prevent status reversion of existing stories.\n    28→\n    29→**Evidence from `ralph/status.json`:**\n    30→- `stories_completed: 70` (should be 74)\n    31→- `stories_remaining: 4` (should be 0)\n    32→- Ralph still believes 4 stories are incomplete\n    33→\n    34→**Fix deployed each session:** Restore 4 stories to `done`, set epic-16 to `done`, update totals from 70 to 74. Sometimes also remove `1-1-foo` phantom.\n    35→\n    36→## Cost Analysis\n    37→\n    38→### Cumulative Sprint Cost\n    39→\n    40→| Metric | Value |\n    41→|--------|-------|\n    42→| Total API-equivalent cost | $716.85 |\n    43→| Total API calls | 5,268 |\n    44→| Average cost per story | $3.54 |\n    45→| Total tokens (all types) | ~299.2M |\n    46→\n    47→### Cost Breakdown by Token Type\n    48→\n    49→| Type | Tokens | Cost | % |\n    50→|------|--------|------|---|"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01QG642JrSPAWw4HDFJ8bezX","session_id":"a168b15c-ec64-44b3-89ac-e9f9d9e07ae8","uuid":"f9b53edd-11bf-40ec-8ec9-49abe1e19dda","timestamp":"2026-03-28T05:50:52.544Z"}
